# About the Project

This repository contains the UI/UX design created in Figma for the GeeksforGeeks RCOEM Chapter.
The goal of the design is to provide students with an intuitive platform to explore events, learning resources, coding activities, and chapter updates.

# Objectives

Create a modern, student friendly interface

Make event discovery and registration simple

Highlight resources, blogs, and achievements

Maintain consistent branding of the chapter

# Features Designed

Landing / Home page

Events & workshops section

Member / team page

Resources & blog layout

Contact & community links

Responsive views (if you made them)

# Design System

Mention things like:

Color palette

Typography

Grid / spacing

Components (buttons, cards, navbars)

